\section{ Why do you want to do PhD/MS / what motivates you for PhD/MS (research)?}
I am J.Uma Mahesh working as a Assistant Professor in the Dept of C.S.E, Since from the year 2009 to till today. My career goal is to receive a Ph.D from IIT’S/NIT’S, and to excel my professional growth. The main thing which motivated me to do Ph.D is teaching and Learning. I believe that always, a teacher is a continuous Learner. So when teacher is erudite in his area of work. He can guide and motivate the students effectively in teaching and learning activities.
