 \subsection*{\textbf{4. Specify a research problem that you would like to attempt (if any).}} \newline
 I would like to continue the work on “Climate Changes and its Environmental Impacts Due to Fast Urbanization”
 \newline
 \newline
 \underline{The objective of this project is to develop the android app which is used to:} \newline
1. Determine the various effects on climate due to urbanization\newline
2. Analyze climate changes due to green house gases of different areas by keeping sensors in the urbanized places and rural places
\newline
3. Use data analytics to draft the climatic conditions with the help of machine learning algorithms
\newline
4. Compare the results of urban and rural areas to know which area is polluted more due to urbanization
\newline
5. Suggest prevention strategies (if any) for those areas
\newline 6. Identify the environmental changes with respect to human ,plants growth, animals and etc

